00:29:04,218 --> 00:29:06,596
Hindi
pa ba sinabi sa iyo ni Cassandra ang susunod mong gawain?

509
00:29:10,232 --> 00:29:12,818
Kailangan mong pumatay ng tatlong tao.

510
00:29:14,153 --> 00:29:15,153
Tatlo?

511
00:29:15,279 --> 00:29:16,447
Ah, huwag kang mag-alala.

512
00:29:16,989 --> 00:29:19,116
Bibigyan ka namin ng sapat na oras para diyan.

513
00:29:22,161 --> 00:29:23,329
Sino sila?

514
00:29:25,748 --> 00:29:26,748
Tingnan natin.

515
00:29:39,595 --> 00:29:40,595
Ha?

516
00:29:41,805 --> 00:29:43,390
Bakit kasama ang nanay ni Aemie?

517
00:29:45,017 --> 00:29:45,661
Para lang sa kasiyahan.

518
00:29:45,685 --> 00:29:48,229
Wala na kaming
ibang maisip ni Meisha.

519
00:29:50,564 --> 00:29:51,564
Sa tingin mo nakakatawa ito?

520
00:29:51,983 --> 00:29:53,317
Ah, bakit hindi?

521
00:29:56,435 --> 00:29:57,435
Bakit hindi?

522
00:29:58,364 --> 00:29:59,532
Kailangan mong patayin silang lahat.

523
00:29:59,849 --> 00:30:00,849
Tama?

524
00:30:02,368 --> 00:30:03,827
Ang kasunduan ay kasunduan.

525
00:30:17,091 --> 00:30:19,093
Malaki ang problema ng kompanya.

526
00:30:19,221 --> 00:30:21,723
Noong nakaraang linggo, dalawang daang milyong piso

527
00:30:21,801 --> 00:30:24,679
misteryosong nawala
sa aming pananalapi.

528
00:30:24,718 --> 00:30:26,284
Dapat sana ay...

529
00:30:26,308 --> 00:30:27,308
Noong nakaraang linggo?

530
00:30:31,089 --> 00:30:33,508
Kung gayon, bakit ngayon ka lang nagpapatawag
ng board meeting?

531
00:30:37,851 --> 00:30:40,936
Responsibilidad mong mag-ulat

532
00:30:40,961 --> 00:30:44,297
lahat ng bagay na may kaugnayan sa
mga bagay na pinansyal ng kompanyang ito,

533
00:30:44,322 --> 00:30:46,866
magandang balita man o masamang balita.

534
00:30:47,713 --> 00:30:49,923
Pasensya na po, Ginang Roswell.

535
00:30:50,986 --> 00:30:52,321
Ipagpatuloy ang talakayan.

536
00:30:52,902 --> 00:30:55,070
Maraming departamento ang naapektuhan.

537
00:30:55,095 --> 00:30:57,181
Umaalis ang mga stockholder

538
00:30:57,423 --> 00:30:59,800
dahil takot silang mawalan ng pera.

539
00:31:00,363 --> 00:31:04,699
Sa ngayon, ang
kita ng kumpanya ay bumaba ng 20%

540
00:31:04,724 --> 00:31:07,257
at 10% sa buong korporasyon.

541
00:31:14,998 --> 00:31:17,125
Kailangan nating gumawa ng paraan tungkol dito.

542
00:31:17,161 --> 00:31:19,003
Kahit ang ibang mga kumpanya ay nagsisimula na rin

543
00:31:19,028 --> 00:31:21,780
para marinig ang
problemang kinakaharap natin.

544
00:31:22,305 --> 00:31:25,892
Ginang Roswell, mayroon ka bang
mga plano para lutasin ito?

545
00:31:40,886 --> 00:31:43,680
Huwag kang gagawa ng anumang hindi kinakailangang
aksyon nang walang pahintulot ko.

546
00:31:44,965 --> 00:31:46,592
Gusto kong magtrabaho kayong lahat

547
00:31:46,944 --> 00:31:48,904
na para bang wala tayong kinakaharap na malaking problema.

548
00:31:49,738 --> 00:31:50,990
Pasensya na po, ginang?

549
00:31:58,510 --> 00:32:01,054
Alam kong mahirap magtrabaho kapag
maraming iniisip.

550
00:32:02,443 --> 00:32:04,238
Pero huwag masyadong isipin ang lahat ng bagay

551
00:32:04,262 --> 00:32:06,447
Naririnig mo ang tungkol sa
mga problema ng kumpanya.

552
00:32:07,243 --> 00:32:10,871
Magpapatawag ako ng isa pang board meeting
bukas ng madaling araw.

553
00:32:12,214 --> 00:32:13,214
Naintindihan?

554
00:32:13,399 --> 00:32:14,399
Opo, ​​ginang.

555
00:32:24,296 --> 00:32:26,624
Patay ako pag-uwi ni Zeke.

556
00:32:27,572 --> 00:32:29,324
Ang dami na niyang
problemang naghihintay sa kanya.

557
00:32:29,348 --> 00:32:31,491
Una, ang huling habilin at testamento.

558
00:32:31,516 --> 00:32:33,184
At ngayon, ito rin.

559
00:32:34,978 --> 00:32:37,022
Paano kung hindi ko na lang sabihin sa kanya?

560
00:32:38,776 --> 00:32:39,735
Hindi, hindi ko kaya.

561
00:32:39,760 --> 00:32:42,887
Sinabi ko sa kanya na sasabihin ko sa kanya
ang lahat ng nangyayari.

562
00:32:44,296 --> 00:32:46,279
Patay na ako.

563
00:33:01,263 --> 00:33:04,850
Ah, kanina noong
pulong ng kumperensya.

564
00:33:06,854 --> 00:33:11,526
May, uh... isang maliit
na problema lang sa kompanya.

565
00:33:11,747 --> 00:33:15,417
Pero huwag kang mag-alala dahil
may aalamin ako.

566
00:33:21,100 --> 00:33:23,728
Hoy, anong nangyayari sa'yo?

567
00:33:25,699 --> 00:33:28,535
Malamang galing
na naman kay Prof. Lim ang gamot mo, 'di ba?

568
00:33:29,213 --> 00:33:31,006
Bakit ka tumatawa
mag-isa diyan?

569
00:33:32,291 --> 00:33:34,460
May problema na ang kompanya mo.

570
00:33:34,655 --> 00:33:35,948
Sige, sabihin mo sa akin.

571
00:33:36,428 --> 00:33:38,764
Ano ba itong maliit na
problema sa kompanya natin?

572
00:33:43,781 --> 00:33:45,033
"Ang kompanya namin," aniya.

573
00:33:46,619 --> 00:33:47,619
Aba, may katuturan naman.

574
00:33:47,644 --> 00:33:50,605
Ako naman si Ginang Roswell kung tutuusin.

575
00:33:52,449 --> 00:33:53,741
Pero bakit ganito?

576
00:33:53,766 --> 00:33:57,226
Alam mo, sa tingin ko
kailangan ko talagang ipa-check ang puso ko.

577
00:33:57,251 --> 00:33:58,294
Dahil

578
00:33:59,138 --> 00:34:03,184
kasi ang lakas ng kabog ng dibdib ko
tuwing kausap ko si Zeke.

579
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:06,835
Namimiss ko ba siya? Parang...

580
00:34:07,592 --> 00:34:09,427
parang gusto ko na
siyang umuwi.

581
00:34:11,241 --> 00:34:12,707
Hoy, babae!

582
00:34:12,923 --> 00:34:14,174
Bakit wala kang sinasabi?

583
00:34:15,162 --> 00:34:16,163
Namimiss ko...

584
00:34:16,357 --> 00:34:17,357
Binibini?

585
00:34:17,798 --> 00:34:18,881
Uy, hoy!

586
00:34:18,906 --> 00:34:19,865
Hindi, sandali!

587
00:34:19,890 --> 00:34:21,627
Hindi ko sinabing nami-miss kita, ha!

588
00:34:22,036 --> 00:34:23,036
Uh. / ...

589
00:34:23,996 --> 00:34:25,623
Sabi ko meron

590
00:34:25,720 --> 00:34:26,720
may ipis!

591
00:34:27,038 --> 00:34:27,831
Oo, isang ipis.

592
00:34:27,856 --> 00:34:28,523
Ayan, tingnan mo.

593
00:34:28,548 --> 00:34:31,799
Kasalanan mo pa naman,
kumakain ka pa ng tsokolate sa loob ng opisina mo.

594
00:34:31,824 --> 00:34:33,344
Kaya ka nagkakaroon ng mga ipis.

595
00:34:36,250 --> 00:34:38,503
Hoy, hoy Dong!

596
00:34:40,539 --> 00:34:41,540
Zeke!

597
00:34:42,606 --> 00:34:43,941
Asawa!

598
00:34:45,442 --> 00:34:46,442
Sabihin mo sa akin.

599
00:34:46,918 --> 00:34:48,920
Ano ba ang maliit na
problema sa kompanya natin?

600
00:34:50,947 --> 00:34:51,948
Ahm ito pala...

601
00:34:53,333 --> 00:34:54,710
Ah...

602
00:34:55,685 --> 00:34:57,824
Nawala ang napakalaking halaga ng pera.

603
00:34:59,649 --> 00:35:02,485
Kaya
bumaba ang kita ng kompanya.

604
00:35:02,879 --> 00:35:03,752
Sige.

605
00:35:03,777 --> 00:35:05,819
Kaya, ano ang plano mo?

606
00:35:05,844 --> 00:35:06,844
Ah...

607
00:35:08,424 --> 00:35:10,843
Iyon nga, wala pa ako niyan.

608
00:35:11,184 --> 00:35:13,228
Uy, pero huwag kang mag-alala dahil

609
00:35:14,469 --> 00:35:16,179
Nag-iisip ako ng mga paraan.

610
00:35:16,231 --> 00:35:17,566
Iyon ang naging
takdang-aralin ko buong araw.

611
00:35:17,590 --> 00:35:18,590
Pangako.

612
00:35:20,367 --> 00:35:20,951
Mabuti.

613
00:35:20,976 --> 00:35:22,519
Uy, Dong.

614
00:35:23,973 --> 00:35:25,015
Galit ka ba?

615
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:28,593
Hindi mo man lang ba ako sesermunan?

616
00:35:29,123 --> 00:35:30,124
Dahil tama,

617
00:35:30,428 --> 00:35:34,223
Nagtrabaho ka nang husto noon para iligtas
ang kumpanya mo mula sa pagbagsak, at pagkatapos...

618
00:35:35,144 --> 00:35:35,761
At pagkatapos...

619
00:35:35,785 --> 00:35:37,230
At ngayon, ito na naman!

620
00:35:41,769 --> 00:35:43,160
Alam mo, masyado kang madaldal.

621
00:35:43,675 --> 00:35:45,719
Mag-focus ka na lang sa pag-iisip kung paano ito aayusin.

622
00:35:46,047 --> 00:35:47,132
Babalik na ako sa bahay.

623
00:35:47,358 --> 00:35:48,358
Talaga?

624
00:35:48,703 --> 00:35:49,703
Kailan?

625
00:35:49,757 --> 00:35:50,757
Malapit na.

626
00:35:56,328 --> 00:35:57,912
Tingnan mo ang bastos na lalaking ito, seryoso.

627
00:35:57,937 --> 00:35:59,897
Bigla niya akong binabaan ng tawag.

628
00:35:59,922 --> 00:36:02,508
Kinakausap ko pa rin siya at tinatanong kung kailan.

629
00:36:06,815 --> 00:36:09,210
Iniisip ko kung ano ang
magiging reaksyon niya kapag nakita niya

630
00:36:09,234 --> 00:36:10,986
kulay rosas lahat ang opisina niya.

631
00:36:12,738 --> 00:36:17,034
Siguro ganito ang magiging reaksyon niya.

632
00:36:19,847 --> 00:36:21,988
Maligayang pagbabalik, Dong!

633
00:36:29,903 --> 00:36:31,059
Ano ang ginawa mo?

634
00:36:31,238 --> 00:36:33,324
Pinakulay mo ng rosas ang opisina ko?

635
00:36:43,648 --> 00:36:44,793
Ang ganda!

636
00:36:45,137 --> 00:36:46,372
Gustong-gusto ko ito!

637
00:36:46,396 --> 00:36:47,689
Ang galing mo!

638
00:36:47,768 --> 00:36:48,768
Talaga?

639
00:36:48,808 --> 00:36:49,767
Nagustuhan mo ba?

640
00:36:49,792 --> 00:36:50,792
Oo, oo!

641
00:36:51,529 --> 00:36:52,529
Alam mo,

642
00:36:53,570 --> 00:36:54,570
paano kung

643
00:36:54,618 --> 00:36:56,579
gagawin nating kulay rosas ang buong gusali?

644
00:36:57,632 --> 00:36:58,632
Ano sa tingin mo, babae?

645
00:36:58,657 --> 00:37:00,533
Diyos ko!

646
00:37:00,558 --> 00:37:01,100
Oo, oo?

647
00:37:01,125 --> 00:37:02,513
Iyon din mismo ang iniisip ko noon!

648
00:37:02,537 --> 00:37:05,749
Pagkatapos ay gagawin nating
kulay rosas ang mga uniporme ng mga guwardiya,

649
00:37:05,994 --> 00:37:08,037
at pati na rin ang lahat ng empleyado!

650
00:37:08,062 --> 00:37:08,938
Oo, oo!

651
00:37:08,963 --> 00:37:09,963
- Tara na!
- Oo!

652
00:37:10,212 --> 00:37:11,212
Dito, Dong.

653
00:37:11,813 --> 00:37:13,523
Handa na ba kayo?

654
00:37:13,715 --> 00:37:14,758
Oo!

655
00:37:15,029 --> 00:37:16,197
Musika!

656
00:38:45,033 --> 00:38:46,401
At kinuha niya ang gusto kong puntahan.

657
00:38:46,425 --> 00:38:47,593
Kambal talaga kami.

658
00:38:49,392 --> 00:38:50,392
Hehe, parang.

659
00:38:52,012 --> 00:38:53,138
Bumagsak ka, bumagsak ka.

660
00:38:53,177 --> 00:38:54,177
Pangunahin.

661
00:38:57,152 --> 00:38:58,278
Alam mo, kung ako 'yon...

662
00:38:58,820 --> 00:38:59,820
Parang ganoon.

663
00:38:59,845 --> 00:39:01,055
Tinuturuan na kita.

664
00:39:01,184 --> 00:39:02,227
Hoy, kuys!

665
00:39:02,500 --> 00:39:03,500
Hoy, babae!

666
00:39:03,761 --> 00:39:05,385
Hoy, kuys!

667
00:39:05,410 --> 00:39:06,286
Uy, bigla mo siyang tinawagan?

668
00:39:06,311 --> 00:39:07,771
Pinsan mo? Pinsan mo?

669
00:39:12,501 --> 00:39:14,145
Kasi, kumusta ang trabaho?

670
00:39:14,169 --> 00:39:15,587
May problema ba?

671
00:39:21,434 --> 00:39:23,353
Ano ang nangyari sa kanya?

672
00:39:31,829 --> 00:39:32,497
Ha?

673
00:39:32,774 --> 00:39:33,774
Hey, Aemie!

674
00:39:36,113 --> 00:39:36,918
Buntong-hininga.

675
00:39:36,943 --> 00:39:38,109
Hayaan mo na lang siya, Momo.

676
00:39:38,134 --> 00:39:39,552
Sa halip, ako na lang ang bigyan mo ng pansin.

677
00:39:39,695 --> 00:39:41,028
Pwede ba tigilan mo na ang pang-iistorbo sa akin?

678
00:39:41,053 --> 00:39:42,053
Naku.

679
00:39:42,259 --> 00:39:44,010
Kaya ayun, kakambal.

680
00:39:44,035 --> 00:39:44,813
Tumahimik ka.

681
00:39:44,838 --> 00:39:46,339
Ang dali lang para sa'yo sabihin na
wala ka ngang love life.

682
00:39:46,363 --> 00:39:47,823
Ikaw rin!

683
00:39:48,837 --> 00:39:50,422
Uy, Amesyl, huwag
mo siyang gawing boyfriend, ha?

684
00:39:50,446 --> 00:39:52,613
Parang gagawin ko siyang boyfriend?

685
00:39:52,638 --> 00:39:53,308
Tara na.

686
00:39:53,333 --> 00:39:54,333
Uri.

687
00:39:54,931 --> 00:39:55,390
Sila!

688
00:39:55,460 --> 00:39:56,460
Ikaw na ang bahala.

689
00:39:56,485 --> 00:39:57,485
Kaizer!

690
00:39:59,297 --> 00:40:00,298
At sino ito?

691
00:40:01,273 --> 00:40:01,734
Oo.

692
00:40:01,758 --> 00:40:02,425
Sino ka?

693
00:40:02,450 --> 00:40:03,450
Relaks ka, pare.

694
00:40:03,642 --> 00:40:05,477
Kaibigan ako ni G. Roswell.

695
00:40:06,043 --> 00:40:06,999
Okay?

696
00:40:07,024 --> 00:40:08,085
- At kaibigan ko si...
- Uhh.

697
00:40:08,109 --> 00:40:09,109
Siya si Kaizer.

698
00:40:09,134 --> 00:40:10,260
Isang mabuting kaibigan ko.

699
00:40:18,066 --> 00:40:19,276
Nakakainis lang ang lalaking ito.

700
00:40:22,988 --> 00:40:24,364
Aaahhh!

701
00:40:35,917 --> 00:40:38,503
♪ Nagsimula akong maniwala sa forever ♪

702
00:40:38,551 --> 00:40:41,401
♪ noong sandaling nakilala kita. ♪

703
00:40:54,225 --> 00:40:56,435
Kasalanan lahat 'to ni Dodong!

704
00:40:56,917 --> 00:41:00,296
Sa halip na isipin ang
dapat kong sabihin sa board,

705
00:41:00,867 --> 00:41:03,722
Iniisip ko tuloy yung text niya!

706
00:41:05,697 --> 00:41:07,901
Dapat ko na bang ipasok ang sarili ko sa
mental hospital?

707
00:41:22,230 --> 00:41:24,253
Baby Ae!

708
00:41:25,896 --> 00:41:26,896
Mama!

709
00:41:28,587 --> 00:41:29,755
Nasaan ang apoy?

710
00:41:30,120 --> 00:41:30,578
Ha?

711
00:41:30,603 --> 00:41:31,479
Nasaan ang apoy?

712
00:41:31,504 --> 00:41:33,588
Hindi ka bulag, baby Ae!

713
00:41:33,613 --> 00:41:35,853
Parang hindi mo ako napansin.
Kanina pa ako nandito.

714
00:41:36,046 --> 00:41:37,339
Bulag ako, mommy?

715
00:41:37,885 --> 00:41:39,929
Paano ako naging bulag?

716
00:41:41,320 --> 00:41:43,114
Dahil ba sa text ni Zeke na nagsasabing.

717
00:41:43,623 --> 00:41:45,542
"Namimiss kita, asawa ko?!"

718
00:41:46,555 --> 00:41:48,924
Naku, baby Ae!

719
00:41:48,949 --> 00:41:50,593
Huwag kang mag-alala.

720
00:41:50,617 --> 00:41:53,954
Sasabihin ko sa iyo kapag may
bagong pelikula tungkol kay Dollie.

721
00:41:55,205 --> 00:41:56,373
Mama!

722
00:41:56,441 --> 00:41:58,735
Ibig sabihin ba niyan ay hindi ko
na makikita si Dollie?!

723
00:42:03,523 --> 00:42:04,232
Hoy!

724
00:42:04,257 --> 00:42:05,878
Anong klaseng drama 'yan?

725
00:42:07,678 --> 00:42:08,678
Kasi.

726
00:42:08,992 --> 00:42:09,992
- Kasi.
- Ah?

727
00:42:10,129 --> 00:42:11,380
Kasi, bulag na ako ngayon.

728
00:42:11,670 --> 00:42:12,670
Bulag?

729
00:42:12,983 --> 00:42:14,735
Pero sa paraan ng iyong paglalakad
na puno ng drama,

730
00:42:14,759 --> 00:42:16,268
ganyan na ba ang mga bulag ngayon?

731
00:42:17,982 --> 00:42:18,982
Kalokohan niyo 'yan.

732
00:42:21,218 --> 00:42:22,218
Mama!

733
00:42:22,243 --> 00:42:23,333
Mama!

734
00:42:23,358 --> 00:42:26,511
Nakakakita na naman ako!

735
00:42:26,556 --> 00:42:27,516
Isa itong himala, mama.

736
00:42:27,541 --> 00:42:29,339
Isa itong himala, nanay!

737
00:42:29,364 --> 00:42:31,074
Isa itong himala!

738
00:42:32,982 --> 00:42:34,066
Pero.

739
00:42:34,411 --> 00:42:36,112
Ano na ang gagawin ko, mama?

740
00:42:36,847 --> 00:42:38,224
Wala pa rin akong plano.

741
00:42:41,129 --> 00:42:42,672
Isang plano para saan?

742
00:42:44,078 --> 00:42:45,542
Kasi mama, alam mo...

743
00:42:45,745 --> 00:42:48,784
Nalugi ang kompanya ni Zeke ng 200 milyong piso.

744
00:42:49,111 --> 00:42:51,425
Sabi nila, malaki ang ibinaba ng kita ng kompanya .

745
00:42:51,577 --> 00:42:54,354
Kung hindi ko ito malutas, nanay,

746
00:42:54,495 --> 00:42:56,873
Hindi ko na alam ang
gagawin ko, Mommy!

747
00:42:57,084 --> 00:42:58,251
Hindi ko talaga alam!

748
00:42:58,276 --> 00:43:00,445
Nawala ba ang malaking halaga ng pera?

749
00:43:00,551 --> 00:43:01,551
Oo.

750
00:43:08,069 --> 00:43:09,069
Alyana.

751
00:43:10,160 --> 00:43:11,787
Malaking halaga na ng
